    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model adequately predicts hemolysis index within uncertainty bounds. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied across all 5 flow-speed operating points. Model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions in the CPB COU.",
